WEBVTT

00:07.340 --> 00:08.466
It was here.

00:08.550 --> 00:12.512
It was just here. Why is it not
here? No! No! No! No! Oh!

00:12.595 --> 00:15.765
Shit. Shit. Shit. It was
here. I swear to God.

00:15.849 --> 00:17.058
Yeah, here we go again.

00:17.142 --> 00:18.560
Another RollerWorld delusion.

00:18.643 --> 00:20.520
No, no, no. I can prove it.

00:20.603 --> 00:23.189
Look. We'll find the perp.

00:26.359 --> 00:28.528
Holy shit! Where did you find it?

00:28.611 --> 00:30.655
- Wait, the green's real?
- RollerWorld's real.

00:32.156 --> 00:33.783
Wait. What was that?

00:33.867 --> 00:35.785
- Yeah, what are you doing?
- Nothing.

00:36.077 --> 00:38.747
Not important. Okay,
okay, we got something.

00:39.414 --> 00:42.250
My parents, who are completely
disrespecting my privacy...

00:42.333 --> 00:44.377
And about to get it in on your bed.

00:44.461 --> 00:46.838
No, they're not about to get it in.

00:47.300 --> 00:48.381
Nah.

00:48.882 --> 00:50.133
Oh, my God.

00:50.717 --> 00:51.730
No.

00:52.010 --> 00:53.762
No, no, no. Stop. Don't do that.

00:54.304 --> 00:56.890
No, no, no, no, no, no!

00:57.930 --> 00:59.120
Here, take it. I can't...

00:59.130 --> 01:00.560
- can't do this.
- Ugh!

01:00.643 --> 01:02.771
- Hmm.
- Ugh, okay.

01:03.521 --> 01:07.067
It's over. Okay. I'll never be
able to look at them again.

01:09.444 --> 01:11.571
Wait. Why is she in my closet?

01:14.866 --> 01:16.785
Mom!

01:20.371 --> 01:21.915
Oh, my doll.

01:21.998 --> 01:25.293
Oh, my God!

01:25.376 --> 01:28.171
- Oh, my God!
- Aren't you guys tired already?

01:28.254 --> 01:30.381
What? You were supposed
to lock the door!

01:34.594 --> 01:36.930
- Wipe it off. Come on.
- We got it.

01:41.050 --> 01:42.184
Hi.

01:42.769 --> 01:43.769
You okay?

01:44.646 --> 01:46.856
Seriously, this whole situation
is potentially scarring.

01:46.940 --> 01:49.192
But I don't have time to get into that.

01:49.984 --> 01:51.050
Where's my gym bag?

01:51.945 --> 01:52.990
With my football gear.

01:53.363 --> 01:54.420
It was in my closet.

01:55.115 --> 01:56.991
Oh, the stinky one.

01:57.420 --> 01:58.450
It's gone.

01:58.743 --> 02:00.537
It's not like you're
playing football anymore.

02:00.870 --> 02:03.039
I needed to get in my
year-end tax deductions,

02:03.123 --> 02:04.124
so I donated it.

02:04.749 --> 02:07.335
You... donated it?!

02:08.100 --> 02:10.520
- Synced & corrected by<font color="#E83286"> MementMori </font>-
